{"tid":1791522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警公佈拉人兩小時後放人","createTime":"2019-12-21T02:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T03:25:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef9ffeb789aff451285fb3fab9b6cee61b9cb6b","tid":1791522,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/ZZ6KOQQCCXYAUHAPY3GMRXVC6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2FZZ6KOQQCCXYAUHAPY3GMRXVC6I%2F&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=d7c91759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2FZZ6KOQQCCXYAUHAPY3GMRXVC6I%2F&h=41c1dcb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/ZZ6KOQQCCXYAUHAPY3GMRXVC6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n警公佈拉人兩小時後放人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576860162_5639.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576860162_5639.gif&h=94c58037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火同盟昨日下午在facebook發帖，表明繼續全力支援抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前日下午高調見傳媒，宣稱支援抗爭者的網上眾籌平台「星火同盟」牽涉洗黑錢活動，拘捕三男一女，但警方未能提出洗黑錢證據，被捕四人更於記者會後兩小時便全部獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月中到警署報到。事件被質疑是政治打壓，星火同盟強調會繼續全力支援因抗爭而被拘捕的人士。<br />\n<br />\n昨下午4時許，星火同盟在facebook發帖，稱被捕人士於前晚7時左右已全部保釋離開警署，強調「平台的被捕支援工作從沒受到影響，定當繼續全力支援因抗爭而被拘捕的人士」。《蘋果》隨即向警方查詢被捕人士的情況，警方在約一小時後發新聞稿，交代被捕的三男一女已獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉案公司地址屬掛名<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：踢保教師轟警濫捕致準則不公<br />\n<br />\n被捕四人包括一名17歲理大學生、兩名分別22歲及28歲一男一女文員，以及一名50歲姓王公司董事。警方前日下午5時許高調見傳媒，指被捕各人涉嫌參與洗黑錢罪行，並稱行動中警方凍結一個7,000萬元的銀行戶口，但其間未有提出實質洗黑錢證據。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方指涉案大部份款項存入一間空殼公司，記者昨根據地址上門，發現是一間秘書公司，主要業務是替不同公司掛名運作，職員稱不清楚案件。據悉早前亦有人員上門調查，但未能撿獲涉案證據後離去。<br />\n<br />\n■記者翁鈺輝"},{"pid":"cc41b2f4d38e8875c3bc7bcabf4ccd6d7d043ad7","tid":1791522,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">杜絕政治酬庸<br />\n銀髮族集會</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間:下午1時至5時<br />\n地點:愛丁堡廣場大會堂對出空地<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\nfacebook銀髮族老而不廢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">毋忘721恐襲<br />\nRemembering 721 Terror</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間 : 15:00<br />\n地點: <br />\n- 元朗 YOНО MALL"},{"pid":"91a61919d10838abbb2b69394ce50e3727d9d362","tid":1791522,"uid":270619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0cmEJN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0cmEJN.jpg&h=5a961d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B61Cc3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB61Cc3N.png&h=fe352b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqVzfha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqVzfha.gif&h=88e16dd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdecabe946d96ae366dbf5ec09c4e224b770572b","tid":1791522,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"51733717a797e734caf09056f5983489e08a7494","tid":1791522,"uid":113155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"高調地拉，低調地放"},{"pid":"e849d01aa4261b781a4191d257e666eaa3e71179","tid":1791522,"uid":202895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"平安無事就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ce0ff121636583aa02958e205e7ee43def6b23","tid":1791522,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc41b2f4d38e8875c3bc7bcabf4ccd6d7d043ad7","tid":1791522,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20